Ok jeff. You present many intetesting points in your videos. I dint watch your videos because i cant bench. I watch some of them, ( and some from others) to see whats trending and any latest information

I dont like to sound like im bragging, but from a starting bodyweught if 145 lbs, ive built up my chrst with benchnpress working up to a max of 585 lbs, lifetime drug free, and im proud of it. Bench is a staple movement, as you said, but its also onebof the most effective chest builders. Biochemical individuality plays a role also. Not saying everyone can build up to a 585 bench.
